Date: Tue, 14 Jul 2026 08:54:39 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Add navigation action ABI

A small bird learned Back and Forward,
And Refresh with crash in view.
It can push state for smoke-born truth,
Then tell the toolbar what is true.
